{"tid":2450401,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過為咗做返運動打止痛針","createTime":"2021-03-17T10:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T15:02:29.000Z","uid":313692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c95363fb9a1fdd9c8379e1e19f492ade759dcb8e","tid":2450401,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"傷膝頭 <br />\n想去返之前嘅運動強度 <br />\n搞咗半年先得7成強度左右<br />\n依家再操甘啲就會痛 但活動能力又冇大影響<br />\n醫生話keep到一個月 <br />\n有冇巴絲試過？"},{"pid":"14cd47bac40eb46886bd1136fcd13d0b1e701e2b","tid":2450401,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"我都係唔做運動會死的人。試過幾次傷腳，最長試過一個半月冇跑步。我會食骨質疏鬆嗰d鈣片同葡萄糖胺加快修復速度，係感覺倒康復快咗"},{"pid":"e460d4e3654422544c071b9b6892d3a09240ecc3","tid":2450401,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14cd47bac40eb46886bd1136fcd13d0b1e701e2b","tid":2450401,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"我都係唔做運動會死的人。試過幾次傷腳，最長試過一個半月冇跑步。我會食骨質疏鬆嗰d鈣片同葡萄糖胺加快修復速度，係感覺倒康復快咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"我係去到一個強度就會痛返 <br />\n之後抖幾日又冇事 無限輪迴咁<br />\n有啲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0494df8cacd8a767ba809b559cf554b1711ebadc","tid":2450401,"uid":8951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"單車機傷唔傷？"},{"pid":"9413f4cddc176d558fa3da7b02876c13cd90a0f5","tid":2450401,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e460d4e3654422544c071b9b6892d3a09240ecc3","tid":2450401,"uid":313692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14cd47bac40eb46886bd1136fcd13d0b1e701e2b","tid":2450401,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"我都係唔做運動會死的人。試過幾次傷腳，最長試過一個半月冇跑步。我會食骨質疏鬆嗰d鈣片同葡萄糖胺加快修復速度，係感覺倒康復快咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"我係去到一個強度就會痛返 